{"tid":2266470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺變種病毒 20A.EU1 肆虐歐洲 專家：未來數月影響全球","createTime":"2020-11-01T10:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T11:17:09.000Z","uid":366655,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c89f6520c6b25812f56fd777284f05321e831c17","tid":2266470,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"目前歐洲疫情仍然不受控，甚至正在惡化。昨日（29 日）有瑞士和西班牙的研究團隊發表一項新研究，指發現自 6 月起，有起源於西班牙的武漢肺炎病毒變種為「20A.EU1」，並指自 7 月以來，西班牙記錄到的新變種的頻率已超過 40%，9 月更在瑞士、愛爾蘭、英國等地方錄得至少 70% 頻率，可謂瘋狂蔓延到整個歐洲大陸。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/lifestyle/gadget-gift-guide/%E8%AE%8A%E7%A8%AE%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-20a-eu1-%E8%82%86%E8%99%90%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%88%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83/ar-BB1aA3j1?li=AABr7VL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Flifestyle%2Fgadget-gift-guide%2F%25E8%25AE%258A%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-20a-eu1-%25E8%2582%2586%25E8%2599%2590%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%2Far-BB1aA3j1%3Fli%3DAABr7VL&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnhy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=92d9da56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/lifestyle/gadget-gift-guide/%E8%AE%8A%E7%A8%AE%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-20a-eu1-%E8%82%86%E8%99%90%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%88%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83/ar-BB1aA3j1?li=AABr7VL</a><br />\n<br />\n英文汁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cnbc.com/amp/2020/10/29/coronavirus-variant-seen-spreading-across-europe-research-says.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Famp%2F2020%2F10%2F29%2Fcoronavirus-variant-seen-spreading-across-europe-research-says.html&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnhy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%